resigning after an abyss of meditation), sheshook her head. What about Nelly Langley? This she answered at once: Langleywas mean and cruel and hated her, and only last year whipped her; she hadwelts all over (uncovering for display her right thigh, which now, at least,was impeccably white and smooth).

